name: Custom Order
description: Send us your favourite book cover and we'll turn it into a custom notebook! Custom rebinding of your book ranges from $25 to $30 depending on the size of the book and the number of pages. We can also help you search for that perfect cover. Email us for more information at office@paperbacknote.com
